sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant RM as RoundManager
    participant DWL as TDispatchWaitingList
    participant RP as ReferencePrecalculator
    participant DIS as Dispatcher
    participant BF as Bridge-Facing Adapter
    participant REG as TContainerRegistry
    participant C as TContainer
    participant S as TSlot

    RM->>REG: inspect dispatch-ready container state
    RM->>DWL: register dispatch-eligible container index
    DWL->>RP: provide ordered dispatch candidate indices
    RP->>REG: resolve container/slot data
    RP-->>DIS: prepare / issue TDispatchAccessRef
    DIS->>S: access dispatch-ready envelope through ref
    DIS-->>BF: expose passive dispatch view/ref
    BF-->>DIS: optional pull observation / consumption report
    DIS-->>C: transition exposure/release state as profile allows
